-- Credit Suisse’s Head of MENA Property Research Moves to Sales
-- B y   Z a i n a b   F a t t a h
-- 2012-02-01T07:42:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-01/credit-suisse-s-head-of-mena-property-research-moves-to-sales.html
Ahmed Badr, Credit Suisse Group AG’s
head of  Middle East  and North Africa property research, has
moved to the bank’s sales team as MENA equity sales specialist.  Dubai-based Badr, who joined the bank in 2008, will be
reporting to the head of MENA equities Wafic Nsouli, the analyst
confirmed in a phone interview late yesterday.  Credit Suisse Group declined to comment when contacted by
Bloomberg yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zainab Fattah in Dubai at 
